00:55:43.576 --> 00:55:44.242 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:55:44.242 --> 00:55:44.530 align:middle line:10%
That's correct, yeah.

00:55:44.530 --> 00:55:45.113 align:middle line:10%
>>CARLSON: OK.

00:55:45.113 --> 00:55:48.230 align:middle line:10%
So there's that 528
relationship again.

00:55:48.230 --> 00:55:49.010 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:55:49.010 --> 00:55:49.593 align:middle line:90%
>>CARLSON: OK.

00:55:49.593 --> 00:55:51.730 align:middle line:84%
But in the yugas,
in the kalpas, it's

00:55:51.730 --> 00:55:54.350 align:middle line:90%
based upon this number 432,000.

00:55:54.350 --> 00:55:58.560 align:middle line:84%
432,000 times 2,
864,000, times 3

00:55:58.560 --> 00:56:02.670 align:middle line:84%
