bit of tweaking and adjustment

00:58:07.080 --> 00:58:09.010 align:middle line:84%
the orbital periods
of all the planets

00:58:09.010 --> 00:58:11.380 align:middle line:84%
will fall into line with
these sacred numbers,

00:58:11.380 --> 00:58:14.620 align:middle line:84%
but none of them
hit exactly, right?

00:58:14.620 --> 00:58:19.430 align:middle line:84%
Now, it's kind of like perhaps--
