00:58:29.560 --> 00:58:31.060 align:middle line:90%
Blump, blump, blump.

00:58:31.060 --> 00:58:33.780 align:middle line:90%
It's not smooth, right?

00:58:33.780 --> 00:58:36.350 align:middle line:84%
I look at the solar
