18.5 miles per second, right,

01:00:25.420 --> 01:00:26.310 align:middle line:90%
18.5.

01:00:26.310 --> 01:00:28.729 align:middle line:90%
Anybody can do the math on it.

01:00:28.729 --> 01:00:30.270 align:middle line:84%
And what you'll see
