01:00:43.990 --> 01:00:47.530 align:middle line:84%
There are a number of
key words and names

01:00:47.530 --> 01:00:49.120 align:middle line:84%
in both the Old and
New Testament that

01:00:49.120 --> 01:00:52.530 align:middle line:84%
have the numerical value
of 666, and they're all

01:00:52.530 --> 01:00:54.750 align:middle line:84%
associated with the
sun one way or another.

01:00:54.750 --> 01:00:56.750 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: How did it take
a negative connotation

01:00:56.750 --> 01:00:58.720 align:middle line:90%
as almost demonic?

01:00:58.720 --> 01:01:01.730 align:middle line:84%
>>CARLSON: Well, OK, a simple
