01:01:14.109 --> 01:01:14.900 align:middle line:90%
>>CARLSON: Extreme.

01:01:14.900 --> 01:01:15.890 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: --extreme view--

01:01:15.890 --> 01:01:16.280 align:middle line:90%
>>CARLSON: It is.

01:01:16.280 --> 01:01:17.238 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: --of the sun.

01:01:17.238 --> 01:01:19.780 align:middle line:10%
>>CARLSON: But on
