01:01:22.340 --> 01:01:25.340 align:middle line:10%
regarding the
variability of the sun.

01:01:25.340 --> 01:01:26.042 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Yes.

01:01:26.042 --> 01:01:28.000 align:middle line:10%
>>CARLSON: And the
